fields.headline: Observer killer sudoku
fields.bodyText: Normal Sudoku rules apply, except the numbers in the cells contained within grey lines add up to the figures in the corner. No number can be repeated within each shape formed by grey lines. For a helping hand call our solutions line on 09068 338 228. Calls cost 60p per minute at all times. Service supplied by ATS. Buy next week's Observer Digital Edition to see the completed puzzle.
